Here are my contributions in Team 99

I was the team lead for team 99.

As team lead I was responsible for creating figma files, setting up GitHub Project, team and repository and assigning tasks to teammates.

I was also responsible for monitoring and taking final decisions on the progress of the design and development team.

I organized meetings to discuss and deliberate on important issues concerning the project.

I was responsible for editing, reviewing and submitting necessary forms, links, documents, resources and presentation.


Here's a link to my assigned tasks on GitHub.
Link:
